ino\n| Episode: \"Discovery at Fourteen\"\n|-\n|''[[Bonanza]]''\n| Ted Hoag\n| Episode: \"The Initiation\"\n|-\n| 1973\n|''[[M*A*S*H (TV series)|M*A*S*H]]''\n| Private Walter/ Wendell Peterson\n| Episode: \"[[Sometimes You Hear the Bullet]]\"\n|-\n| 1974\n|''[[The Waltons]]''\n| Seth Turner\n| Episode: \"The Gift\"\n|-\n| 1974\u20131984\n|''[[Happy Days]]''\n| Richard 'Richie' Cunningham\n| 171 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1974\n|''Locusts''\n| Donny Fletcher\n| rowspan=\"3\" | TV Movie\n|-\n|''The Migrants''\n| Lyle Barlow\n|-\n| 1975\n|''[[Huckleberry Finn (1975 film)|Huckleberry Finn]]''\n|[[Huckleberry Finn (character)|Huckleberry Finn]]\n|-\n| 1975-1981\n|''[[Insight (TV series)|Insight]]''\n| Connie/Joe\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1976\n|''[[Laverne & Shirley]]''\n| Richie Cunningham\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n|''I'm a Fool''\n| Andy\n| TV Movie\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1980\n|''[[The Fonz and the Happy Days Gang]]''\n| Richie Cunningham\n| Voice role;<br>Episode: \"King for a Day\"\n|-\n|''[[Act of Love (1980 film)|Act of Love]]''\n| Leon Cybulkowski\n| rowspan=\"3\" | TV Movie\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1981\n|''[[Bitter Harvest (1981 film)|Bitter Harvest]]''\n| Ned De Vries\n|-\n|''[[Fire on the Mountain (1981 film)|Fire on the Mountain]]''\n| Lee Mackie\n|-\n| 1983\n|''When Your Lover Leaves''\n| {{N/a}}\n| TV Movie;<br>Uncredited\n|-\n| 1986\n|''[[Return to Mayberry]]''\n| Opie Taylor\n| rowspan=\"2\" | TV Movie\n|-\n| 1988\n|''Channel 99''\n| Himself\n|-\n| 1998\u20131999\n|''[[The Simpsons]]''\n| Himself\n| Voice role;<br>2 episodes: \"[[When You Dish Upon a Star]]\" & \"[[Hello Gutter, Hello Fadder]]\"\n|-\n| 1999\n|''[[Frasier]]''\n| Stephen\n| Voice role;<br>Episode: \"Good Samaritan\"\n|-\n| 2003\u20132006;<br>2013; 2018\n|''[[Arrested Development (TV series)|Arrested Development]]''\n| Narrator<br>Semi-fictional version of himself\n| 68 episodes\n|-\n| 2016\n|''[[The Odd Couple (2015 TV series)|The Odd Couple]]''\n| Stanley\n| Episode: \"Taffy Days\"