leberry Finn (character)|Huckleberry Finn]]\n|-\n| 1975-1981\n|''[[Insight (TV series)|Insight]]''\n| Connie/Joe\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1976\n|''[[Laverne & Shirley]]''\n| Richie Cunningham\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n|''I'm a Fool''\n| Andy\n| TV Movie\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1980\n|''[[The Fonz and the Happy Days Gang]]''\n| Richie Cunningham\n| Voice role;<br>Episode: \"King for a Day\"\n|-\n|''[[Act of Love (1980 film)|Act of Love]]''\n| Leon Cybulkowski\n| rowspan=\"3\" | TV Movie\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1981\n|''[[Bitter Harvest (1981 film)|Bitter Harvest]]''\n| Ned De Vries\n|-\n|''[[Fire on the Mountain (1981 film)|Fire on the Mountain]]''\n| Lee Mackie\n|-\n| 1983\n|''When Your Lover Leaves''\n| {{N/a}}\n| TV Movie;<br>Uncredited\n|-\n| 1986\n|''[[Return to Mayberry]]''\n| Opie Taylor\n| rowspan=\"2\" | TV Movie\n|-\n| 1988\n|''Channel 99''\n| Himself\n|-\n| 1998\u20131999\n|''[[The Simpsons]]''\n| Himself\n| Voice role;<br>2 episodes: \"[[When You Dish Upon a Star]]\" & \"[[Hello Gutter, Hello Fadder]]\"\n|-\n| 1999\n|''[[Frasier]]''\n| Stephen\n| Voice role;<br>Episode: \"Good Samaritan\"\n|-\n| 2003\u20132006;<br>2013; 2018\n|''[[Arrested Development (TV series)|Arrested Development]]''\n| Narrator<br>Semi-fictional version of himself\n| 68 episodes\n|-\n| 2016\n|''[[The Odd Couple (2015 TV series)|The Odd Couple]]''\n| Stanley\n| Episode: \"Taffy Days\"\n|-\n| 2017\n|''[[This Is Us]]''\n| Himself\n| Episodes: \"What Now?\", \"Deja Vu\", \"Vegas, Baby\"\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{{main|List of awards and nominations received by Ron Howard}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Year\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Work\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| Academy Awards\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| BAFTA Awards\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| Golden Globe Awards\n|-\n! Nominations\n! Wins\n! Nominations\n! Wins\n! Nominations\n! Wins\n|-\n|1982\n|''[[Night Shift (1982 film)|Night Shift]]''\n|\